		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Does the TV have problems with other systems that use a 240-scanline non-interlaced ("240p") mode?  The NES's image is not interlaced.  You can also test out a SNES, Genesis, N64, or even a Wii running a NES emulator to get a non-interlaced 240 scanline picture.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


