	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Some TVs' aspect ratio buttons might not work in HD modes (720p, 1080i, 1080p). Look for an aspect ratio button on the converter. Or try setting the converter to 480p mode instead of 1080p and letting your TV upscale it the rest of the way; TVs are more likely to support 4:3 on SD resolutions than on HD.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
